}

{\pard \fi-360 \li720 \ls68 
\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li720\ri0\fi-360\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 (2) Usually, instructions of work were given to him by an employee of BQIH in Hong Kong known by the name of "Ah Sui" \u65288\?"\u38463\?\u27700\?"\u65289\? . Ah Sui would inform Chan by phone in the evening of the time and place for loading the Lorry in Hong Kong on the following day.\par}
