\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li720\ri0\fi-360\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 (1) Ah Sui was an employee of BQIH (mistakenly stated as Chan). He only relayed the instructions given by SLY to Chan. BQIH did not have any authority to give instructions to Chan.\par}
