\par}

\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 51.} It is noticed that Tsang SC did not deny Chan's account that the aforesaid notice dated 18 November 2011 was given to him by employees of BQIH.\par}

\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li0\ri0\fi0\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 {\f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 52.} Liao EH said in paragraphs 17 to 21 of his supplemental statement that:- {\par}{\pard \fi-360 \li720 \ls75 
