\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li720\ri0\fi-360\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 (2) At that time SLY had signed a contract with UPS agreeing to provide 2 lorries with drivers, one lorry for day shift and the other lorry for night shift, for providing transportation services to UPS. Chan was one of these drivers deployed for the UPS contract.\par}
